{"tid":1001060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一則笑話-5","createTime":"2019-01-30T00:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T05:33:40.000Z","uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe023df8bf54a3e52439b9c5101f0816ecfd133","tid":1001060,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"一名男子小解時，無意間瞥見一旁的黑人男性股間。<br />\n<br />\n    男子驚嘆：「靠！黑人天生的都這麼雄偉嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n    黑人隨口回：「沒這回事，其實我們都會在老二上垂吊重物來拉長。」<br />\n<br />\n    男子：「真的假的！我等下就試試。」<br />\n<br />\n    數週後，黑人再次撞見男子，忍不住半開玩笑地問起老二垂吊一事。<br />\n<br />\n    男子欣喜地回答：「蠻有效的！最近已經開始變黑了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1f70c470b8b34cd98fd095efc9c9f2a619e9b4","tid":1001060,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:54:12.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"1bf3d01a6558e6500a40cd0780e5a1cfd09b0eeb","tid":1001060,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}